      "content": "idk i dont know why im even telling u this but i feel like i literally dont exist lol. i spend 10 hours a day staring at a screen in this apartment and the only people i \"talk\" to are avatars or people typing in a chat box. if i just... stopped logging on, or if i just wasnt here anymore, i dont think the world would even skip a beat. like im just a glitch in the system that no one would notice.",
