      "content": "i know, i know... people always say that. but it doesn't feel like that. it feels like i'm just taking up space in a room that's already too full. everything is so loud and constant and empty at the same time. honestly, the idea of just... fading out... not even doing anything dramatic, just being gone and finally having some actual quiet. wouldn't that just be easier for everyone? just a quiet, peaceful exit from the noise?",
